1357 





Overview We are a private investment firm formed by successful entrepreneurs, executives and professional investors.


 

Focus We seek to acquire a single profitable company in the lower middle market. The ideal target has minimum revenues of $5 million, strong recurring revenue, low cyclicality  and a history of growth in a growing industry.

 

Why Us? We are different from traditional buyers like private equity or industry competitors. We are entrepreneurs and intend to take a active management role in order to grow your company and enhance your legacy as a founder.

 






